data.description: 2 minutes from Hwy 55. Nice home on 1.39 acres. 1 car attached garage and a 2 car carport. 29 x 10 green house attached to the home. Large kitchen, partially finished basement. Steel siding and stone, maintenance free. Newer vinyl windows (2006), Newer Roof (2006), Newer doors (2006). Large yard. Good condition. Refrigerator, range, washer and dryer all stay. Brokered And Advertised By: Signature Properties Listing Agent: Kimberlin Adams
